title: Vinton Street 1-bed+ // South Boston // Sept. 1st

posting_body: ['South Boston 1-bed+ office //', 'Newly Renovated //', 'Top Floor unit!', 'Property Features:', '- Available Sept. 1st 2022 (or sooner!)', '- Great South Boston location close to Andrew Square (Redline T) and Carson Beach/ Castle Island!', '- Top floor unit, approx.', '900 Sq.', 'ft. of living space', '- Newly updated with carpeted dining area and both bedrooms, new windows, fresh paint throughout, new kitchen with track lighting, and an updated bathroom.', '- Bedroom 1 = 8\'-6" x 7\'', "- Bedroom 2 (primary) = 9'x10'", '- Oversized living room with a bump-out window overlooking Vinton Street', '- Hardwood floors, and a ceiling fan in living room', '- Spacious layout', '- Primary bedroom at the rear of the apartment, with the bonus office space in the front of the building.', '- Excellent natural light throughout', '- Free laundry in basement (Free, not coin-operated shared with other 2 units in building) along with extra storage.', '- Fenced, grassy rear yard (shared)', '- Gas cooking and heating.', 'Air conditioners by window ACs', '*Sorry, NO pets!', '$2,600/month (no utilities included)', 'Available July 1st (or sooner)', 'First, security deposit, and 1-month brokerage fee due at lease signing', 'VIDEO TOUR AVAILABLE!', 'To schedule a tour, please call/text or email:', 'James Riel', 'JR Associates | Residential Brokerage', 'james @ jrassociates.co', '#boston #southie #Southboston #forrent #rental #apartment #lease #jrassociates']
